## Spacing Guidelines

- Use generous padding: `p-6`, `p-8` for containers
- Add vertical space between sections: `space-y-6`, `space-y-8`
- Sidebar width: `240px` (fixed)
- Header height: `56px` (h-14)

---

## Typography

- Use Tailwind's default font stack
- Clear hierarchy: `text-xl` for titles, `text-sm` for body
- Semibold for emphasis: `font-semibold`
- Gray scale for text: `text-gray-900` (primary), `text-gray-600` (secondary)

---

## Colors (App Shell)

**Avoid custom colors. Use Tailwind defaults:**
- Backgrounds: `bg-white`, `bg-gray-50`, `bg-gray-100`
- Text: `text-gray-900`, `text-gray-600`, `text-gray-500`
- Borders: `border-gray-200`, `border-gray-300`
- Interactive: `hover:bg-gray-100`, `hover:text-gray-900`

---

## Key Principle

**When in doubt: less is more. Remove rather than add.**
